query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'mathoverflow',
'ru')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-studio',
'at.algebraic-topology',
'c++11',
'css',
'gn.general-topology',
'graph-theory',
'html5',
'pr.probability',
'python',
'real-analysis',
'swift',
'windows',
'вёрстка',
'многопоточность',
'регулярные-выражения')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Caucus',
'Commentator',
'Editor',
'Enlightened',
'Good Answer',
'Informed',
'Necromancer',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Teacher') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
